LYRICS:-
M- तोहार रोजे रोजे बढ़ता बिल धनिया !
हमार देही के धड़कता दिल धनिया !!
F- जाड़ा में आड़ा देवरा तापतावे हीटर !
लगवादी राजा जी !
लगवादी राजा जी हमार लहंगा में मीटर !!!

आन्तरा
F- कबनो बहाना कके ताना रउआ मारिले,
सबकर खीस पिया हमरे प झाड़ी ले !
M- हम जाके बाहरा में करतानी नौकरी,
तू घरे सिंगार कके बनतारु  छोकरी !
F- पानी हे जवानी प गरमावे कई लीटर !
लगवादी राजा जी !
लगवादी राजा जी हमार लहंगा में मीटर !!!

आन्तरा
F- खोसे ला पलक बरियारी रोजे बोड मे,
माने ना खेसारी हमे डाल देता लोड मे !
M- खर्चा उरेब कके जेब कैलू खाली हो,
अब जनि कहिया ह की चाही ओठलाली हो !
F- माने ना बेदर्दी रहे घरवा के भीतर,
लगवादी राजा जी !
लगवादी राजा जी हमार लहंगा में मीटर !!! END

khoon  so jalave gori tera hasna,,

Yuji Itadori is a boy with tremendous physical strength, though he lives a completely ordinary high school life. One day, to save a classmate who has been attacked by curses, he eats the finger of Ryomen Sukuna, taking the curse into his own soul. From then on, he shares one body with Ryomen Sukuna. snippet.title: HACKER OR WHAT | JONATHAN IS BACK!! | BGMI!
snippet.description:
Today, I’m going LIVE from Comic-Con Bangalore for the Google Play Squad Tournament Vip Edition! 🔥
This stream is all about real-time squad action with Google Play VIP members, intense matchups, and high-pressure gameplay straight from the tournament floor.
I’ll be joined with LoLzZz Gaming, and together we’re jumping into a competitive squad battle you don’t want to miss.
⏰ Live Today from 2:00 PM onwards
📍 Streaming directly from Comic-Con Bangalore
Come hang out, watch the matches unfold live, and be part of the action.
See you on stream! 🎮🔥
Hey Guys, I’m Jonathan Amaral, better known as Jonathan Gaming, a professional BGMI esports athlete and streamer.

Since the start of my journey, my dedication to the game has been defined by precision, consistency, and an unstoppable grind. As an assaulter, I’ve built a reputation for clutch performances and high-impact gameplay, earning respect in the BGMI community. 

Through years of dedication, I’ve honed my skills, adapting to every challenge and evolving with the game. Whether in high-stakes tournaments or streaming for the gaming community, my focus remains the same - pushing the limits and delivering top-tier gameplay.

snippet.title: Avengers: Doomsday - Trailer (2026) Marvel Studios (Concept Version)
snippet.description:
— Attention Viewers ⚠️
— This is a Fan-Made Concept Trailer for:
— Avengers: Doomsday

— Music Credits - https://youtu.be/6Ot-gRruxng

— This video is a fan-made concept trailer, created solely for artistic and entertainment purposes.The goal behind this trailer is to showcase my creativity and storytelling skills through a concept trailer based on a unique and original idea. By combining various effects, sound design, and AI technologies, I’ve crafted a cinematic experience that reimagines familiar worlds in bold and imaginative ways. This trailer is not official and is intended to entertain, inspire, and engage with the YouTube community. Thank you for your support — now let’s dive into a world shaped by creativity and craft. 🎬✨

— In this concept trailer for Avengers: Doomsday, the story centers on the long-unresolved consequences of Steve Rogers’ final choice in Endgame, revealing that his decision to remain in the past fractured reality in ways the Avengers never anticipated. As timelines splinter and the stability of the main MCU begins to erode, Steve is forced back into the conflict, confronting the personal cost of his legacy and the ripple effects of his sacrifice. The narrative hints at a corrupted alternate reality where familiar heroes took darker paths, drawing Doctor Doom into the heart of the multiversal crisis and threatening total collapse across worlds. With time itself no longer trustworthy, Rogers emerges as both the cause and the possible solution, facing a reckoning that could determine whether the prime timeline survives or is rewritten forever.
